Banks take 2-3 days. Personal loan companies are faster (24-48 hours). Licensed money lenders can approve same-day.

**Step 6: Sign agreement & get funds**
Once approved, you'll sign a loan agreement. Funds typically hit your account within 24 hours after signing.

